      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are sound and it has passed recent inspections, the exterior shows some age with minor dings and paint fading in spots. The interior has visible wear on the upholstery and a few non-essential plastic components show their age, but all primary features remain functional. It's a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price point.",
