    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver with plenty of character? This car is a fantastic find for anyone seeking a functional vehicle at a great price! It's in fair condition, showing some honest wear and tear from its journeys, but it\u2019s ready to keep you moving. If you appreciate a car that\u2019s been used and loved, this is the perfect opportunity to get behind the wheel of a dependable ride!",
