    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating a commitment to mechanical excellence and aesthetic care, the car offers a refined driving experience characterized by smooth performance and a well-preserved interior. Each component has been thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our standards for reliability and prestige. This is a distinguished selection for those who prioritize both value and sophistication in their next automotive acquisition.",
