    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun to drive? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been a total gem. It runs like a dream and has been well-cared for, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s in great shape and totally ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see this go to a good home! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is this driver-focused E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, offering precise shift gates and mechanical engagement. Performance is anchored by a factory limited-slip differential and a rigid chassis that has undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul to ensure thermal efficiency during spirited driving. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and interior bolster wear typical of a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical vitals remain robust with linear power delivery and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. An exceptional opportunity to own a pinnacle of analog M-division engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Recent service complete. Title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example of its class, balancing reliable performance with a clean aesthetic. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side rear bumper\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronic features, including the panoramic sunroof, dual-zone climate control, and the premium infotainment system, are fully functional. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has followed a strict maintenance schedule with a recent full fluid flush and brake pad replacement performed just 2,000 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts crisply without hesitation. It sits on a set of premium tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle perfect for someone who values mechanical integrity and a sharp appearance without the 'mint' showroom price tag.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
